'''拉姆加希亚邦加'''（Ramgarhia Bunga）是印度[[阿姆利则|阿姆利则]][[金庙|金庙]]建筑群的两座叫拜楼风格的锡克[[瞭望塔|瞭望塔]]，高三层，红色砂岩建造。<ref name=pht1/> 它位于不老花蜜水池（Harmandir Sahib Sarovar）东侧的池畔环路（parikrama），隔水池中央的金庙，与水池西侧的[[永恒王座|永恒王座]]（Akal Takht）相对<ref>{{cite book|author1=Pashaura Singh|author2=Louis E. Fenech|title=The Oxford Handbook of Sikh Studies|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=8I0NAwAAQBAJ&pg=PA435|year=2014|publisher=Oxford University Press|isbn=978-0-19-969930-8|page=435|access-date=2020-11-14|archive-date=2021-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204002126/https://books.google.com/books?id=8I0NAwAAQBAJ&pg=PA435|dead-url=no}}</ref>。它是由锡克勇士、拉姆加希亚酋长贾萨·辛格·拉姆加希亚建于18世纪后期<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://sikhchic.com/article-detail.php?id=2532&cat=14 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2020-11-14 |archive-date=2021-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210303201525/https://www.sikhchic.com/article-detail.php?cat=14&id=2532 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.sikh-heritage.co.uk/heritage/Amritsar/Amritsar.htm |title=存档副本 |access-date=2020-11-14 |archive-date=2020-02-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200207152615/http://www.sikh-heritage.co.uk/heritage/Amritsar/Amritsar.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。1762年，艾哈迈德沙·杜兰尼率领的阿富汗穆斯林部队摧毁和亵渎了锡克教圣地。<ref name=pht1/> 此后，锡克人建造瞭望塔，派驻哨兵监视敌情，保护圣地建筑群免受亵渎。<ref name=pht1>[http://punjabtourism.gov.in/Downloads/Brochures/Golden%20Temple%20Amritsar%20Darbar%20Sahib.pdf The Golden Temple] {{Wayback|url=http://punjabtourism.gov.in/Downloads/Brochures/Golden%20Temple%20Amritsar%20Darbar%20Sahib.pdf |date=20210929030058 }}, Punjab Heritage and Tourism Promotion Board, Government of Punjab, India</ref>

瞭望塔内有一块花岗岩加冕石板，取自德里[[红堡|红堡]]的[[孔雀宝座|孔雀宝座]]。<ref>https://www.punjabitribuneonline.com/2016/05/%e0%a8%9c%e0%a9%b1%e0%a8%b8%e0%a8%be-%e0%a8%b8%e0%a8%bf%e0%a9%b0%e0%a8%98-%e0%a8%b0%e0%a8%be%e0%a8%ae%e0%a8%97%e0%a9%9c%e0%a9%8d%e0%a8%b9%e0%a9%80%e0%a8%86-%e0%a8%a6%e0%a9%80-%e0%a8%85%e0%a8%a8/</ref>。锡克教徒进攻[[莫卧儿帝国|莫卧儿帝国]]军队，远征德里，德里的锡克教徒从[[孔雀宝座|孔雀宝座]]上拆除这块皇帝加冕石，将其带回[[阿姆利则|阿姆利则]] 象征莫卧儿帝国即将灭亡<ref name=pht1/>，。

